column6: S.H.I.E.L.D. Briar Raleigh. Red Skull. Nazi Officer Hitzig. As Magneto forges ahead, building his new stronghold amidst the ashes of Genosha, he banishes every demon who might prevent him from completing his mission. But he may find that some demons are more persistent than others...
column8: | writer:Cullen Bunn | artist:Gabriel Hernandez Walta | penciller (cover):David Yardin
